metadata.title: UK High Commissioner calls on DPM Dar, views exchanged over recent regional developments

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, April 26 (APP): British High Commissioner Jane Marriott Saturday called on Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar. During the meeting, they exchanged views on the recent regional developments, Foreign Office Spokesperson said in a press release. The DPM/FM reaffirmed Pakistan's commitment to safeguarding its national interests while ensuring regional peace and security.
